    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402710/extras/6224bee749538ec4ab9f22c7e19b89b6.avif?t=1744141342\" width=616 height=134 /></span><strong>闲置纸牌游戏，有不同的纸牌和不同的牌组。卡牌可以通过不同方式升级。卡组有不同的原型：点击、土、冰、太阳等！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >强大的公会</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402710/extras/4f6164fe619a1d20588d6b8635ee4a28.poster.avif?t=1744141342\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402710/extras/4f6164fe619a1d20588d6b8635ee4a28.webm?t=1744141342\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402710/extras/4f6164fe619a1d20588d6b8635ee4a28.mp4?t=1744141342\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>选择正确的公会会对游戏产生重大影响。公会在每场游戏中都会变得更加强大。从各种公会中进行选择，以支持您的卡组原型。每个公会等级都会获得奖励，达到黄金等级后，奖励将永久伴随您！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >英雄</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雇佣最适合你游戏风格的英雄。选择合适的英雄与你的公会相结合，会让你更上一层楼。打开英雄插槽，创建英雄团队！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多用途游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402710/extras/c9a0e12f84bab342be6818dbf2092a88.avif?t=1744141342\" width=616 height=398 /></span>用扑克牌杀死怪物，获得金钱打开宝箱。 每个箱子都有自己的扑克牌！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了获取卡牌和击杀怪物，游戏中还有许多辅助活动。例如：魔法、炼金术、锻造、任务、资源收集等等。</p>",
